%p
  Login with facebook:<br />
  = link_to image_tag('facebook.png'), '/auth/facebook'

%p
  Don't want to use facebook? No problem. Just contact me and I'll make an account for you.<br />
  If you already have such an account, login below.

- form_for Player.new, :url => session_path, :method => :post do |f|
  = f.label :name
  = f.text_field :name
  %br
  = f.label :password
  = f.password_field :password
  %br
  = f.submit 'login'
